Ahmad Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Ahmad is recorded 640,388 times globally, ranking it as the 29th most common name worldwide.

Ahmad is most prevalent in Saudi Arabia, with 87,285 occurrences, making it the 15th most popular name in the country.
